Heini Arch LVM Rescue ISO

This live environment is based on the official Arch Linux releng profile.

Included LVM helpers:
  /root/lvm-scripts/
  lvm-math-inspect
  lvm-move-space-safe

Recommended first checks:
  lsblk -f
  lvs -a -o+devices
  vgs
  findmnt

For encrypted LVM systems:
  cryptsetup open /dev/<device> <name>
  vgchange -ay

For Arch installation guidance:
  Installation_guide
